Author: KaozTiposta
Title: [ANN] [YTN] YouToken - help entrepreneurs and investors find each other
Body: Youtoken Webinar webinar.youtoken.io  YouToken, CoinStarter, and TokenStars: The Future of the Blockchain Crowdfunding Industry.  The volume of the crowdfunding market totals billions of dollars. A wide variety of people, (ranging from world celebrities to unknown entrepreneurs) use this type of fund-raising method.  As a result, it looks like the landscape is set for a big change. How will this industry progress in 2018? What’s waiting for us?  Cryptocurrencies have been vigorously evolving all throughout 2017 and now they are an integral part of the various spheres of humanity. Of course, crowdfunding is not an exclusion. It is with cryptocurrency that many experts associate the future of crowdfunding. The peer-to-peer technology has revolutionized the way we cooperate with each other. What was impossible in the past due to many restrictions is now easily accomplished. Cryptocurrencies make it possible for investors to connect with entrepreneurs in a transparent and easy way.  To understand all the nascent trends of blockchain-based crowdfunding, we invite you to the webinar that the Youtoken team will host this Thursday, on the 1st of March.  For whom this webinar will be useful Cryptocurrency and blockchain fans Crowdfunding enthusiasts People who are interested in trading financial assets VCs: those who want to support newly born “Elon Musk's”  What you'll learn How blockchain technology will change the crowdfunding industry and what benefits you may get How human intelligence can be converted into a financial asset What projects there are for investors to support and what opportunities they present  The date and time This live webinar takes place on Thursday, March 1, 2018 10 a.m. EST Learn more and sign up at webinar.youtoken.io
